what's a quick easy meatloaf recipe meatloaf ingredients lb ground beef or ground turkey cup italian bread crumbs to eggs depending on consistency small onion finely chopped tsp garlic powder cup green pepper finely chopped cup tomato sauce divided directions combine above ingredients using only half of the tomato sauce and one egg if mixture isn't moist enough add the other egg shape mixture into a loaf and place on a greased cookie sheet or in a meat loaf pan take the remaining tomato sauce and spread on top of meat loaf bake at f for hour for variations you can use barbecue sauce or ketchup instead of tomato sauce as a topping barbecue sauce will give it an extra kick Hamburger Japanese cuisine D__ner kebab Hot dog MRE Chili con carne Tofu Cajun cuisine Bread French fries Sandwich Bengali cuisine Bagel Cantonese cuisine Ketchup Breakfast Peruvian cuisine Cuisine of Brazil Soul food Dumpling McDonald's Cuisine of the Southern United States Sauce Potato chips Jewish cuisine Cuisine of the Philippines In-N-Out Burger German cuisine Pasta Kebab Haggis Fish and chips Salad Gyros Cuisine of Singapore Meatball French cuisine Dim sum Ramen Roman eating and drinking Burger Russian cuisine Polish cuisine Mayonnaise Cincinnati chili Chicken soup Cha chaan teng Domesticated turkey Cuisine of Laos Cuisine of Canada Idli Sushi Grilled cheese sandwich Italian cuisine Nabemono Coffee Gumbo Full English breakfast Cuisine of Vietnam Cheesecake Tamale Cuisine of Malaysia Soup Cheesesteak Rice pudding Gazpacho Cuisine of Thailand Vegetarianism Cuisine of Argentina Donburi Dolma Soy protein Salsa (sauce) Worcestershire sauce Jiaozi Chicago-style pizza Chile pepper Bolognese sauce Cooking Canadian Chinese cuisine Muffin Corned beef Flour Bacon Chicken Pot Noodle Cholent 